author: Kuokka77
description:
"Steps on Tundra" (2000) by Yehar.
Amiga art "At the Riverbank OR Entering the Cave" (read more below) by Jok/Dreamweb, 1st at Gerp 2018 Amiga gfx compo.

On Demozoo the art is titled "Entering The Cave". If you download the release from there and read the included txt file, it very clearly calls this "At the Riverbank". There's no caves in the image, but there is a riverbank. So the latter title makes much more sense to me.

FastTracker 2.1x (8bitbubsy) and AWE64 Gold.
title: FastTracker music: Yehar - Steps on Tundra (AWE64 Gold)
